lender.name: brands
lender.occupational_info: Acuity Brands introduces ROAM, its new revolutionary streetlight monitoring system that delivers high energy savings and reduced maintenance costs. ROAM represents a complete transformation in how street lighting and other outdoor lighting systems are monitored and maintained. It enables proactive and efficient resolution of issues and errors the minute it occurs – eliminating the need for citizens to report or complain. ROAM functions by utilizing an intelligent photocontrol with an embedded communication chip for each light fixture. This allows the fixture to report attributes errors and location for easy monitoring. Once installed, these photo controls can communicate with other photo controls, essentially creating a mesh network. This results in a self-configuring and self-healing outdoor wireless light control system. ROAM has already reduced streetlight outages in some areas for up to 90%. It has also cut street lighting energy costs and carbon emissions by half. This translates to a big improvement in customer satisfaction and in revenue generation. ROAM makes streetlight monitoring so easy yet so effective for municipalities and utilities.
